1942年前，Gr.38 Hl[[高爆反坦克彈|高爆反坦克彈]]是[[四號坦克|四號坦克]]有效应战[[T-34坦克|T-34中型坦克]]的唯一手段<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/239176772|title=Россия и Германия: История прошлого сотрудничества|last=Широкорад|first=Александр Борисович|date=2007-01-01|publisher=Veče|year=|isbn=9785953321914|location=|pages=|chapter=Rossija i Germanija : istorija voennogo soperničestva|oclc=239176772|access-date=2017-05-02|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918214752/https://www.worldcat.org/title/rossija-i-germanija-istorija-voennogo-sopernicestva/oclc/239176772|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，[[希特勒|希特勒]]在[[巴巴羅薩行動|巴巴羅薩行動]]伊始却下令没有他亲自命令，禁止擅自使用Gr.38 Hl<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://ftr.wot-news.com/2013/06/15/historical-heat-ban/|title=Historical HEAT Ban|accessdate=2017-05-02|author=Silentstalker|date=2013-06-15|publisher=For the Record|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630172046/http://ftr.wot-news.com/2013/06/15/historical-heat-ban/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/17871883|title=The Halder War Diary 1939-1942|last=Halder|first=Franz|last2=Burdick|first2=Charles|last3=Jacobsen|first3=Hans-Adolf|date=1988-01-01|publisher=Presidio Press|year=|isbn=9780891413028|location=|pages=|chapter=|oclc=17871883|access-date=2017-05-02|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918214752/https://www.worldcat.org/title/halder-war-diary-1939-1942/oclc/17871883|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原因在于他担心（他认为）先进的[[锥形装药|空心装药]]技术落入[[苏联|苏联]]之手<ref name=":0" />，显然他并不知道苏联当时已经掌握了同类技术<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ww2data.blogspot.com/2015/08/soviet-explosive-ordnance-76mm.html|title=WW2 Equipment Data: Soviet Explosive Ordnance - 76mm Projectiles (Part 3)|accessdate=2017-05-02|date=2015-08-03|last=Fett|first=Jobbo|work=WW2 Equipment Data|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306235108/http://ww2data.blogspot.com/2015/08/soviet-explosive-ordnance-76mm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

